SUMMARY:Claudette Club | AI Build Day
LOCATION:Creative Collective\, Austin\, TX
DESCRIPTION:Source: Luma\n\nBuild Your AI Team: Claudette Club\n\nA monthly
  build day for female founders.\n\nImagine having an executive assistant\,
  content strategist\, community manager\, or operations coordinator suppor
 ting your business without hiring anyone.\n\nAt Claudette Club\, we'll hel
 p you build custom AI teammates inside Claude that save time\, reduce over
 whelm\, and help you get more done.\n\nThis is a hands-on working session 
 where you'll learn\, build\, and leave with AI tools you can start using r
 ight away.\n\nYou'll:\n\n✨ Learn how to think in AI teammates\n\n✨ Bui
 ld your first (or next) AI teammate\n\n✨ Create custom instructions and 
 knowledge files\n\n✨ Get support and feedback as you build\n\n✨ Connec
 t with other female founders\n\nBring:\n\n💻 Your laptop\n\n💡 A busin
 ess challenge\n\nCome build with us.\n\nAbout Creative Collective\nCreativ
 e Collective is a female founder house designed to help women build and gr
 ow their businesses through community\, resources\, programming\, and supp
 ort. It’s a space for founders to connect\, take action\, and grow along
 side women who are building too. @creativecollectiveatx\n\nCalendar: Creat
 ive Collective\n\nHosts: Creative Collective\, Toria Bonanni\, Brigitte Do
 novan\n\nVenue: Creative Collective\n\nEvent page: https://luma.com/creati
 ve-h4dv
URL:https://luma.com/creative-h4dv
STATUS:CONFIRMED
TRANSP:OPAQUE
END:VEVENT
