SUMMARY:The Health Hustlers: An Exclusive Networking Event for Health/Welln
 ess Professionals
LOCATION:2043 S Lamar Blvd\, Austin\, Texas
DESCRIPTION:Source: Luma\n\nJoin us for an evening of meaningful connection
  and collaboration for anyone who works in the health\, wellness\, or fitn
 ess space here in Austin.\n\nWhether you’re part of a wellness-focused b
 usiness\, contribute to a health-oriented team\, or simply play an active 
 role in helping others improve their well-being\, this event is for you. H
 ealth Hustlers ATX is a space to build real relationships with people who 
 understand your passion for helping others live better\, healthier lives.\
 n\nWho Should Attend:\n\nHealth\, Wellness & Fitness Professionals\n\nAnyo
 ne who works in the health\, wellness\, or fitness industry and wants to c
 onnect with others in the community. There’s no requirement to be an own
 er or founder — just someone actively involved in the field.\n\nGrowth-O
 riented Individuals\n\nYou’re interested in collaborating\, sharing idea
 s\, learning from others\, and expanding your circle within Austin’s wel
 lness landscape.\n\nCommunity-Driven People\n\nYou appreciate authentic co
 nnection over transactional networking and want to be part of a supportive
 \, positive environment.\n\nPlease Note:\nThis is not a sales-driven or pi
 tch-focused event. We encourage open conversation\, genuine connection\, a
 nd collaboration.\n\nWhat to Expect:\n\nA relaxed\, welcoming environment 
 that makes meeting new people easy\n\nMeaningful conversations about healt
 h\, wellness\, and personal growth\n\nUnique formats that encourage real c
 onnection\, not awkward small talk\n\nOpportunities to build long-term rel
 ationships and collaborations\n\nItinerary:\n\n6:30–7:00 p.m. — Meet &
  Greet 🤝\n7:00–7:45 p.m. — Small Group Icebreakers 🧊\n7:45–8:0
 0 p.m. — Speed Networking 🏃‍♂️\n8:00 p.m. — Group Photo 📸\
 n8:00-8:30 p.m. — Friendworking 🤠\n8:30 p.m. — Goodbyes! 👋\n\nLi
 mited spots available. Please register in advance to secure your place.\n\
 nWe look forward to connecting with you and continuing to strengthen Austi
 n’s wellness community together!\n\nReach out to Dr. Scott at drscott@li
 mitlesschiroatx.com with any questions.\n\nCalendar: Health Hustlers ATX\n
 \nHosts: Dr. Scott Mitchell\, Corey Hiben\n\nVenue: 2043 S Lamar Blvd\n\nE
 vent page: https://luma.com/bf8v2qhs
URL:https://luma.com/bf8v2qhs
STATUS:CONFIRMED
TRANSP:OPAQUE
END:VEVENT
