SUMMARY:Beans & Builders Founder Meetup
LOCATION:Cosmic Pickle\, Austin\, TX
DESCRIPTION:Source: Luma\n\nBeans & Builders is a relaxed\, informal meetup
  put on by Austin Founders Feed\, bringing local founders together to conn
 ect\, swap stories\, and learn from each other over some good coffee.\n\nR
 eal conversations about the wins\, the problems\, and everything in betwee
 n. To keep things flowing\, we'll have a few light prompts and topics on h
 and so the conversation never gets stale\, covering Marketing & Growth\, P
 roduct\, Systems & AI\, and Funding (bootstrapping vs. raising money).\n\n
 Our goal is simple: get to know this community better and give founders a 
 space to share what they're working on and what they're stuck on. Come as 
 you are\, grab a cup\, and meet some of the people building in Austin.\n\n
 The first few to arrive get a little something from us\, so it pays to be 
 early. See you there.\n\nBeans & Builders is hosted by Austin Founders Fee
 d\, a free newsletter covering the founders\, startups\, and stories shapi
 ng Austin.\n\nCalendar: Austin Founders Feed\n\nHosts: Ken Jee\, Warren\n\
 nVenue: Cosmic Pickle\n\nEvent page: https://luma.com/gjp5hy8r
URL:https://luma.com/gjp5hy8r
STATUS:CONFIRMED
TRANSP:OPAQUE
END:VEVENT
