SUMMARY:Trail Talks #5
LOCATION:111 Congress Ave.\, Austin\, TX
DESCRIPTION:Source: Luma\n\nAlright\, we're back for a summer edition of Tr
 ail Talks. Yes\, it's the week after July 4th\, but let's be honest: the l
 ong weekend leaves a mark… and this is the perfect blend of "I'm still d
 oing work" without having to sit behind a desk.\n\nWe're keeping our featu
 red founder and investor under wraps until one week before the walk\, so s
 tay tuned for the reveal.\n\nMoving forward\, we're also going to be featu
 ring a charity every week. This walk we'll hear from Andrea Olvera with CA
 SA - an incredible group of volunteers that advocate for children who’ve
  experienced abuse or neglect as they navigate the court system.\n\nAs alw
 ays\, you'll be in great company: founders\, investors\, and startup folks
  who show up curious\, generous\, and ready to swap ideas.\n\nRemember to 
 bring your friends! We'll see you out there!\n\nSincerely\,\n\nPat (https:
 //lonestartup.com) & Sam (https://www.hill-climbers.com) (we do startup po
 dcasts)\n\nCalendar: Personal\n\nHosts: Patrick Killoren\, Samuel Huntingt
 on\, Stephen Cunningham\n\nVenue: 111 Congress Ave.\n\nEvent page: https:/
 /luma.com/og6mt8s2
URL:https://luma.com/og6mt8s2
STATUS:CONFIRMED
TRANSP:OPAQUE
END:VEVENT
