SUMMARY:Chapter 2: Let’s Get Spicy | AnniversaryPoolside Reader Social
LOCATION:Austin\, TX
DESCRIPTION:Source: Luma\n\nJoin us for our biggest reader social yet as we
  celebrate two years of Keep Austin Romantic!\n\nSpend the evening connect
 ing with local romance readers while enjoying a curated summer experience 
 at a private luxury vacation rental in the heart of Travis Heights. Whethe
 r you’re swimming\, lounging poolside with a book\, crafting custom keep
 sakes\, enjoying dinner\, or simply making new friends\, this event is des
 igned to bring readers together beyond the page.\n\nWhether it’s your fi
 rst Keep Austin Romantic event or your fifteenth\, we’d love to welcome 
 you.\n\nYour Ticket Includes\n\n🌮 Catered Tex-Mex fajita buffet\n\n🕶
 ️ DIY sunglasses and keychain craft bar\n\n📸 Professional photography
  throughout the evening\n\n📚 Bookish games\n\n🍓 Desserts & Prosecco 
 popsicles\n\n🎁 Goodie bag\n\n🏊 Poolside fun\n\n🧖 Sauna & cold plu
 nge\n\n📖 Reading nooks and indoor lounge spaces\n\nThe Venue\n\nCelebra
 te with us at a beautiful private luxury vacation rental tucked away in th
 e heart of Travis Heights.\n\nEnjoy:\n\nResort-style pool & lounge areas\n
 \nSauna & cold plunge\n\nBeautiful spaces & photo moments\n\nIndoor & outd
 oor lounge areas\n\nSwim\, lounge\, read\, craft\, and celebrate\, all in 
 one beautiful space.\n\n🔒 The exact address and parking instructions wi
 ll be emailed to ticket holders before the event.\n\nWhat to Know\n\n🩴 
 Bring: A towel\, swimsuit\, sunscreen\, and your current read if you’d l
 ike to relax poolside.\n\n🌮 Included: Catered fajita buffet\, desserts\
 , sparkling refreshments\, water\, and bubbly. BYOB is welcome!\n\n❄️ 
 Need a break from the heat? Plenty of beautiful indoor lounge space with A
 /C is available throughout the event.\n\n💖 Whether it’s your first me
 etup or your fifteenth\, we’d love to have you.\n\n18+ ONLY\n\n🎟️ T
 ickets\n\nEarly Bird — $55\nAvailable June 26 through July 5 (or until s
 old out)\n\nStandard Admission — $65\nBeginning July 6\n\nAttendance is 
 intentionally limited so every guest has plenty of room to swim\, lounge\,
  craft\, and enjoy the entire experience.\n\nSpecial Thanks\n\nA huge than
 k you to our incredible partners for helping bring this celebration to lif
 e.\n\n🏡 Via Luxury Rentals for hosting us in one of their beautiful lux
 ury vacation homes.\n\n📸 Channing Stark Photography (@seeing_spirit_pho
 tog) for capturing all the memories from our anniversary celebration.\n\nW
 e can’t wait to celebrate the next chapter with you. ❤️\n\nCalendar:
  Keep Austin Romantic\n\nHosts: Mina A\, Meggan\n\nEvent page: https://lum
 a.com/2tsqr2wo
URL:https://luma.com/2tsqr2wo
STATUS:CONFIRMED
TRANSP:OPAQUE
END:VEVENT
