SUMMARY:Antler's Summer Bash and Hot Ones Challenge with Rho!
LOCATION:Austin\, TX
DESCRIPTION:Source: Luma\n\n🔥 Beat the heat (or don't) at Antler's Summe
 r Bash!\n\nJoin us for good food\, drinks\, and great conversation. The ma
 in event? A spicy twist on networking\, our Hot Ones Challenge. Founders e
 arn the chance to grill our very own\, Jake O'Shea\, one fiery wing at a t
 ime.\n\n🌶️ The Hot Ones Challenge:\n\nHere's the deal\, founders get 
 to put Jake in the hot seat\, no question off-limits\, but there's a catch
 . To earn your question\, you've got to eat a wing at the same heat level.
  We'll climb the Scoville scale\, starting mild and ending with a finale t
 hat hits 8 MILLION SHU. (For reference\, that's well past pure chili extra
 ct territory and into "are you sure about this?" range.) The hotter the wi
 ng\, the bolder the question.\n\nWhether you're a founder\, builder\, oper
 ator\, or just getting your startup off the ground\, come connect with the
  people building alongside you.\n\nSchedule\n\n5:00-8:00 PM - Networking\n
 \n6:00-7:00 PM - Hot Ones Challenge\n\nBring your toughest questions and y
 our highest spice tolerance. See you there! 🔥\n\nMeet your Hosts: \n\nA
 ntler: \n\nAntler is an early-stage venture capital firm with a focus on i
 nception stage founders and a community of resident tech entrepreneurs and
  operators. Founders are immersed in a community with everything they need
  to build and scale at lightning speed. If you're building\, we want to he
 ar about it!\n\nRho\n\nFrom two-person startups to public companies\, ​
 ​​Rho is the banking platform with everything businesses need to manag
 e cash\, control spend\, and automate finance busywork. Rho offers corpora
 te cards\, banking\, treasury\, expense management\, AP\, accounting autom
 ation\, and more in one integrated platform backed by award-winning suppor
 t.\n\nRho is a fintech company\, not a bank. Checking and card services pr
 ovided by Webster Bank\, N.A.\, member FDIC\; savings account services pro
 vided by American Deposit Management\, LLC\, and its partner banks.\n\nCal
 endar: Antler US\n\nHosts: Melissa Lichota\, Jake O'Shea\, Akhil Aneel\, P
 rerna Sharma\n\nEvent page: https://luma.com/antlerus-jm6b
URL:https://luma.com/antlerus-jm6b
STATUS:CONFIRMED
TRANSP:OPAQUE
END:VEVENT
