 novation leaders for an evening of big ideas\, rapid-fire pitches\, and re
 al connections across the ecosystem.\n\nAttendees will hear from entrepren
 eurs and emerging companies as they share what they’re building\, what p
 roblem they’re solving\, and why it matters. Whether you’re looking fo
 r your next collaborator\, customer\, investment\, or inspiration\, Launch
  Pad is built to help you plug into the community and meet the people shap
 ing what’s next in Texas startups.\n\nThis event is free and open to any
 one interested in the innovation ecosystem.\n\nFor those ready to pitch\, 
 Launch Pad also gives founders and aspiring entrepreneurs a chance to take
  the mic and compete for prizes:\n\nGrand Prize: 3-month coworking members
 hip\n\nRunner-Up: 1-month coworking membership\n\nWe’ll also have light 
 bites and drinks\, with updated food offerings designed to create a better
  networking experience. Need a headshot? We've got you!\n\nInterested in p
 itching? Email memberships@stationaustin.org\n\nCalendar: STATION Austin\n
 \nHosts: STATION Austin\n\nVenue: 701 Brazos St\n\nEvent page: https://lum
 a.com/ykwfywxt
