DESCRIPTION:Source: Luma\n\nJoin us for a special AustinJS night dedicated 
 entirely to AI Workflows!\n\nOn this AustinJS open mic night\, come and sh
 are how you've been interacting with AI tools and workflows. Don't know wh
 at to talk about but want to participate? Here are a couple of ideas:\n\nB
 uilding with AI (Product & Tech): Built an autonomous agent\, deployed an 
 LLM-powered feature\, or shipped a clever AI workflow? Show us the tech st
 ack\, the architecture\, and how it works under the hood.\n\nBuilding Fast
 er with AI (Dev Productivity): Developed a killer prompt workflow\, paired
  up with local models\, or customized your IDE to write code at warp speed
 ? Pull up a terminal and show us your daily setup.\n\nMeetup Schedule:\n6:
 00 - 7:00 -> Food and networking\n7:00 - 8:00 -> AI Workflow Presentations
 \n8:00 -> Walk to Zilker Brewing Company and hangout\n\nCome and give a ta
